      <p><strong>Please note that we do not run any frontline services.</strong> Please check for suitable organisations in the <a href="/find-help/">Find Help</a> section if you are experiencing homelessness and need support.</p>

      <h2 class="h2">Charities and Voluntary Groups</h2>
      <p>If you are a Manchester based organisation, and would like your services to be listed, changed or removed, please let us know at <a href="mailto:admin@streetsupport.net">admin@streetsupport.net</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="h2">Corporate Partners</h2>
      <p>If you are a business that share our values and would like to support our mission, please contact <a href="mailto:sponsorship@streetsupport.net">sponsorship@streetsupport.net</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="h2">General Questions</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions, ideas, or would like to know more about us, you can get in touch at <a href="mailto:info@streetsupport.net">info@streetsupport.net</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="h2">General Updates</h2>
      <p>You can join the conversation on <a href="https://twitter.com/streetsupportuk">Twitter</a> or <a href="https://www.facebook.com/streetsupport/">Facebook</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="h2">In person</h2>
      <p>You are welcome to come and visit us in person at Together, 127 Portland St, Manchester, M1 4PZ. We are often out and about so please contact us first by emailing <a href="mailto:info@streetsupport.net">info@streetsupport.net</a>, or you can contact Gary by phone on 07824 667709.</p>

